  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <q>Mientras jugaban, ¿cuáles pistas fueron las que más les ayudaron y por qué?</q>  (Knowing how the mystery number would round to the nearest ten was really helpful because that really narrowed it down. Knowing the numbers the mystery number was between was helpful if it was something like 150 and 160, but not if it was between 100 and 200.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


